 />\n對<br />\n但佢通常都煮到好鹹<br />\n應該係個廚師問題"},{"pid":"1deb2343c06965e2fd7a0df83d54287226cf362a","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪去鋪頭問請唔請人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對呀<br />\n不過我覺得唔好做"},{"pid":"fa09b9ee6d189cf29f69f8bbc86dc5225634d63a","tid":322074,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:19:46.000Z","msg":"廚房點整野食"},{"pid":"2d63596d976991d28088550fa518a69d224d494d","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廚房點整野食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd食物pack好一包包<br />\n佢地都係加熱"},{"pid":"d0f57b1132e6ce62f35e9b0e89a1bb942215512a","tid":322074,"uid":124838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"Pt時薪幾多？"},{"pid":"ffc3109375238107e5a68aae05db4747caea8ca9","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pt時薪幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n43至50都有"},{"pid":"43d8702215f42f1635774522c54c936ec9ff2c3b","tid":322074,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"朗豪坊？"},{"pid":"fdbe44ffb89b5e0aa74afbb9aa08afcfe4712c0b","tid":322074,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"到底係茶定係木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c924a32dcfd718e5be04340f6f453928e96f6b65","tid":322074,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"007eb0b7981776c61f8ba7f6ae2c579d3166db95","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朗豪坊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"