,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地啲飲品太甜，尤其是啲水果沙冰<br />\n但係啲野食幾好食，分量都唔會太少</blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你問我答變左食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能佢以為水吧同廚房整嘢係關樓面事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果學似你話齋你除左樓面咩都唔知的話。<br />\n咁區區一個樓面waiter仲有乜好問姐？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔多唔少都會知大約既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果問飲品點沖就真係淨係知好多都係果醬汁唧出黎溝<br />\n廚房材料真係好多現成切好包好"},{"pid":"519de007924dedbd8411011258e2dfd8cadc6cb8","tid":322074,"uid":46788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"樓主邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會係同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都做緊pt"},{"pid":"2ce1842b457a2b293b9299d464a618a9c8ba9ef7","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會係同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都做緊pt</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我辭咗職啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ce1d19b7e185177eb9b267621666512aba8ead","tid":322074,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺間野好撚難食"},{"pid":"529cd5ad82cfb51b1113d2c23d873badb0f81d0e","tid":322074,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"磚塊好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db79f184149dd78fba6a705b7ebe91a2ccb41a1","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺唔覺間野好撚難食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲難食<br />\n但有啲我覺得幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce5f408ea0d0491eaf1383aab7bbb7dfdf7a8a5","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>磚塊好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時會太甜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且食得多都悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee307baa94735fc7e4ed89372b22fa6b1a581e1f","tid":322074,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"我都做緊 不過就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4561426f2251ed8f099c3648ed50fc46616907","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都做緊 不過就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分享下原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c68e8dd959fe180f1526a5da4c7b64837e14117","tid":322074,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"想做水吧"},{"pid":"0764982b4a3744abc4940ac689c9f1e202f7bb77","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想做水吧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想<br />\n不過個時個經理話水吧夠人<br />\n但原來呃我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9739af2756f4d1f01e4e31f15648ff2f1e61877","tid":322074,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n去過不下二十次 有十次以上有漏單或錯單<br />\n有幾個員工掛住傾計或望女基本上停住工作"},{"pid":"506a4946e4aec6c871e034fcb4d112a33403f5aa","tid":322074,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>磚塊好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時會太甜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且食得多都悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n70 蚊好貴 但又成日想食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254dce15ce8acc6a4621f9565c06075c1931155d","tid":322074,"uid":21976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾<br />\n去過不下二十次 有十次以上有漏單或錯單<br />\n有幾個員工掛住傾計或望女基本上停住工作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少漏單 通常係廚房做得慢<br />\n其實正常要覆單<br />\n所以我未試過錯單<br />\n好叻叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD老屎忽full time成日傾計係真<br />\n之後就話我唔做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}